## Common Patterns
**Loading state:**
```typescript
const [isLoading, setIsLoading] = useState(false);
// Use SkeletonLoading component for UI
```

**Toast notification:**
```typescript
showToast("Message", "success" | "error" | "info");
```

**Modal pattern:**
```typescript
const [isOpen, setIsOpen] = useState(false);
{isOpen && <ModalComponent onClose={() => setIsOpen(false)} />}
```

